I. SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
II. INSTALLING AND COMPILING




=========================================================
I. SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS 
=========================================================

- c++ compiler (g++, icc, etc)


=========================================================
II. INSTALLING AND COMPILING
=========================================================

Modify the Makefile for your particular system (compiler, linker, etc), and run the following commands:

tar -xvf jscience.tar
make clean
make 


